<plot>Journey into America's primitive soul in this documentary about the resurgence of humanity's oldest and most intense rituals. From garden-variety tattooing, to frenzied effigy-burning festivals, to the disturbing extremes of body-piercing, Modern Tribalism explores the cultural context surrounding this underground movement.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?374085</url></doc>
